metadata.name: FVCK 12
metadata.description:
A state trooper standing guard in front of a boarded building with the words Fuck 12 graffitied. 

Pretty much the sentiment of the city after George Floyd was murdered in the hands of the MPD. 

These Editions are in the loving memory of Geroge Floyd
